        <ul class='ms-4 list-disc text-muted-foreground'>
          <li>Researching on Diffusion Models and 3D Vision.</li>
          <li>Contributed to <strong>Project: Optical Boundary Recognition</strong>.</li>
        </ul>
      </Card>
      <Card
